body_html:
The code doesn't work in tf-nightly for me. What code did you run that works in TF 1.4?

FWIW, the failure in tf-nightly is due to the current lack of tf.SparseTensor support. See this Stack Overflow answer for some workarounds:

https://stackoverflow.com/a/46732695/3574081

The code doesn't work in `tf-nightly` for me. What code did you run that works in TF 1.4?

FWIW, the failure in `tf-nightly` is due to the current lack of `tf.SparseTensor` support. See this Stack Overflow answer for some workarounds:

https://stackoverflow.com/a/46732695/3574081
